headline: GE HealthCare names Jeannette Bankes president and CEO, Patient Care Solutions
summary: CHICAGO, April 09, 2025--GE HealthCare (Nasdaq: GEHC), a leading global healthcare solutions provider, announced the appointment of Jeannette Bankes as president and CEO, Patient Care Solutions, effective May 1, 2025.
